1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
CMD: "turn fifteen degrees right"

2
00:00:05,490 --> 00:00:10,490
CMD: "and move forward until I say stop"

3
00:00:39,990 --> 00:00:44,990
Robot: "There is too much lag time for me to wait for you to tell me to stop.  About how far would you like me to move forward after turning 15 degrees right?"

4
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:54,350
CMD: "fifteen feet"

5
00:00:59,990 --> 00:01:04,990
Robot: "executing..."

6
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:46,640
Robot: "I moved forward as far as I could after turning right."

